description: Phat Thai is a hearty + heartfelt homestyle Thai cookin' food truck hitting the SF Bay Area streets. Keep posted for the latest updates on this new venture!Wanna tuk with us?One of the newest additions to the SF Bay Area food truck scene, we offer hearty and heartfelt authentic Thai food.The project, started by brothers Bobby and Alom Hossain, brings Chef Wannee's (aka Mom) cooking from our kitchen to your street curb!
name: Phat Thai
